name: Long Double Loop Necklace
description:
LOOP plays with an essential element in jewelry: the eternal loop. Sometimes pure, sometimes linked, they form various pieces. The loops are soft, made from chain and change shape when you move. They sparkle with numerous facets that reflect the light. There are pieces in silver and others with a color transition from light silver fading into dark grey. The dark part almost dissolves when you wear it on a dark fabric. The material is Sterling Silver. 

Long necklace out of two loops that change shape as you move. Engraved label in the back that connects the two loops.

Product images and description, courtesy of Saskia Diez.

name: Big Knot Necklace No.1
description:
Short necklace with 2 knots that hide a mechanism to adjust the length of the necklace. Adjustable length of the necklace from appr. 40 (or shorter) - 60cm. Sterling silver. 

Product images and description, courtesy of Saskia Diez.

name: Big Knot Necklace no.5 (Oxidized Sterling Silver)
description:
Long necklace with 2 knots and tassels. You wear it like a scarf in different ways. 

Only available in oxidized sterling silver. Image of product in sterling silver is for reference only.

Product images and description, courtesy of Saskia Diez.

name: Rose Gold Wire Ring
description:
Simple, fine and very delicate ring made out of 18 karat gold wire, in rose gold. The wire is 0.7mm.

Product images and description, courtesy of Saskia Diez.

name: Loop Ring
description:
LOOP plays with an essential element in jewelry: the eternal loop. Sometimes pure, sometimes linked, they form various pieces. The loops are soft, made from chain and change shape when you move. They sparkle with numerous facets that reflect the light.

A simple loop with a twist, you double it and slip it on your finger. The material is boxchain made from sterling silver, with its surfaces sparkling in the light. 

Product images and description, courtesy of Saskia Diez.
